OL,3,CUK braces for Storm Dave as 80mph
OL,4,Cwinds expected to disrupt Easter travel
OL,6,FThe UK is bracing for the impact of
OL,7,FStorm Dave, with gale-force winds
OL,8,Fexpected to disrupt travel across the
OL,9,FEaster weekend.
OL,11,FFour Met Office yellow warnings are in
OL,12,Fplace from Saturday, covering all of
OL,13,Fmainland Scotland, Northern Ireland,
OL,14,Fparts of northern England and North
OL,15,FWales.
OL,17,FThose travelling during the warning
OL,18,Fperiod have been told there could be
OL,19,Fdisruption on the roads as well as on
OL,20,Frail, air and ferry services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
