OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775311858
OL,3,CUK braces for Storm Dave as 80mph
OL,4,Cwinds expected to disrupt Easter travel
OL,6,FWind speeds could reach up to 80mph in
OL,7,Fsome areas, and there could also be
OL,8,Fdangerous conditions from large waves
OL,9,Falong the coastline.
OL,11,FWhat Met Office warnings are in place?
OL,13,FThe Met Office also warned there could
OL,14,Fbe "injuries and danger to life from
OL,15,Fflying debris" and said some areas
OL,16,Fmight experience power cuts.
OL,18,FNorthern Scotland will also experience
OL,19,Fheavy rain and snowy conditions on
OL,20,Fhigher ground.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
