OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775311858
OL,3,CUK braces for Storm Dave as 80mph
OL,4,Cwinds expected to disrupt Easter travel
OL,6,FStorm Dave will hit hardest on
OL,7,FSaturday evening, before beginning to
OL,8,Fweaken on Sunday as it moves into the
OL,9,FNorth Sea.
OL,11,F"A rapidly deepening area of low
OL,12,Fpressure, Storm Dave, will cross
OL,13,FScotland on Saturday night before
OL,14,Fclearing into the North Sea on
OL,15,FSunday," the Met Office's forecast
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
