PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775311858
OL,3,CUK braces for Storm Dave as 80mph
OL,4,Cwinds expected to disrupt Easter travel
OL,6,F"Whilst some uncertainty remains in
OL,7,Fthe exact track and shape of Storm
OL,8,FDave, a spell of strong south-westerly
OL,9,Fwinds is expected. Gusts of 50-60mph
OL,10,Fare expected fairly widely with 60-
OL,11,F70mph in more exposed locations.
OL,13,F"The strongest winds are expected
OL,14,Fduring Saturday evening where there is
OL,15,Fa small chance of gusts of 70-80mph
OL,16,Fbriefly, particularly northern England
OL,17,Fand southern Scotland.
OL,19,F"Large waves may lead to some
OL,20,Fdangerous conditions around windward
OL,21,Fcoasts."
