OL,3,CUK braces for Storm Dave as 80mph
OL,4,Cwinds expected to disrupt Easter travel
OL,6,FBreakdown service RAC has predicted
OL,7,Fthis year will be the busiest Easter
OL,8,Fon the roads since 2022.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FTravel trade organisation Abta has
OL,16,Falso estimated that two million people
OL,17,Ffrom the UK will travel abroad between
OL,18,FGood Friday and Easter Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
