OL,3,CUK braces for Storm Dave as 80mph
OL,4,Cwinds expected to disrupt Easter travel
OL,6,FThose driving in Scotland have been
OL,7,Furged to check their journeys before
OL,8,Fsetting off.
OL,10,F"Storm Dave is a timely reminder that
OL,11,Fwe can face challenging weather
OL,12,Fconditions at any time of year, not
OL,13,Fjust during the winter period," said
OL,14,FGeorge Fiddes, from Transport Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
